    "body": "Hey @yesezra—we don't plan to create a Places connector. I recommend creating your own Places widget based on [the one that we provide](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/dd0ad2ca8f7db5017c90f05dc1cd22bc1f3dcab4/src/widgets/places/places.ts).\r\n\r\nYou can copy/paste it (minus the TypeScript specifics), you'll have access to the `init` and `dispose` lifecycle methods.\r\n\r\nClosing this but feel free to reopen if you need further guidance.",
